<PlaybookLayout
  title="Pricing Your Dev Product for Maximum Revenue"
  metaTitle="Pricing Your Developer Product for Maximum Revenue | CodeToCash"
  metaDescription="Pricing models, psychology, and strategy for indie developers and vibe coders. How to price your SaaS, tool, or template to maximize revenue."
