      </div>
      <div class="p-3 bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/5 rounded-lg">
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-1">For monthly subscriptions:</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-green-400 font-mono">"Start Building — Cancel Anytime"</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-3 bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/5 rounded-lg">
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-1">For annual plans:</p>
